e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.enterpr1se.info/2016/01/telegram-so-fun-and-safe/</a><br />\n<br />\n我用Telegram 原因好簡單:<br />\n1.訊息,圖片,影片儲存在雲端,多客端訊息會同步,換機不用備份訊息跟多媒體.<br />\n2.群組上限5000人,超級群,新成員可以瀏覽群組成立至今的訊息.<br />\n3.在群組內,陌生人看不到他人電話,只能看暱稱及Telegram id(ID可不設定).<br />\n還有很多,不寫出來,有待自己發掘.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>網購谷：</strong><br />\n淘寶： <a href=\"https://t.me/taobaocouponsharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftaobaocouponsharing&d=nzSJVo1IAPnrs9zyhenr%2BQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=6eea0642\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/taobaocouponsharing</a><br />\n亞馬遜/其他： <a href=\"https://telegram.me/webbuy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.me%2Fwebbuy&d=nzSJVo1IAPnrs9zyhenr%2BQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=1fa4e2e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://telegram.me/webbuy</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>lihkg小本創業谷/b]：<br />\n<a href=\"https://telegram.me/lihkgbiz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.me%2Flihkgbiz&d=nzSJVo1IAPnrs9zyhenr%2BQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=c3620e21\" target=\"_blank\">https://telegram.me/lihkgbiz</a><br />\n<br />\n[b]潮流谷</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://telegram.me/HKhypegroup\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.me%2FHKhypegroup&d=nzSJVo1IAPnrs9zyhenr%2BQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=ec3dbfe2\" target=\"_blank\">https://telegram.me/HKhypegroup</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://telegram.me/HKbuysellgroup\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.me%2FHKbuysellgroup&d=nzSJVo1IAPnrs9zyhenr%2BQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=419a1542\" target=\"_blank\">https://telegram.me/HKbuysellgroup</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>攝影谷:</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/PhotographyHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FPhotographyHK&d=nzSJVo1IAPnrs9zyhenr%2BQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=82e49313\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/PhotographyHK</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>電影谷</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://telegram.m